snippet.title: [Trailer for STEAM] The Insider – interactive movie(ENG sub)
snippet.description:
[Trailer for STEAM] The Insider – interactive movie(ENG sub)

The Insider is a thrilling chase action film of a whistleblower who wants to dig out corruption and reveal it to the world. The Insider is an interactive film where a viewer’s choices decide how the story goes. It has five different endings and her fate depends entirely on your choice.

Google Play Store
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.inters.ins

STEAM
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1304620/The_Insider__interactive_movie/
